Package com.github.crashdemons.playerheads.api

Class HeadRepresentation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.crashdemons.playerheads.api.HeadRepresentation
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CustomHeadRepresentation
    public class HeadRepresentation
extends java.lang.Object
    Interface for an object containing the information that is used to compare and construct a head based on type and owner. This information explicitly excludes details like the texture which are not considered part of head equivalence.
    Since:
    5.2.2-SNAPSHOT
    Author:
    crashdemons (crashenator at gmail.com)
